  "description": "Fix Typography Issues on Registration Page\n\nResolve typography and text rendering problems on the o-przedszkolu/zapisy/ (About Preschool/Registration) page.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify all typography issues on the /o-przedszkolu/zapisy/ page (font sizes, weights, line heights, spacing, alignment)\n- Ensure text is readable and properly formatted across all sections\n- Check for consistency with typography styles used elsewhere on the site\n- Verify proper font family application and fallbacks\n- Fix any text overflow, wrapping, or truncation issues\n- Test typography rendering across different browsers and viewport sizes\n- Ensure proper contrast ratios for accessibility compliance\n- Check Polish language characters render correctly (including diacritics: ą, ć, ę, ł, ń, ó, ś, ź, ż)",
